<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>Wireframe Halaman Homepage - Layanan Konsultasi Kesehatan</title>
<style>
  body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 1rem;
    background: #fff;
    color: #222;
  }
  h1 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .wireframe-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .block {
    border: 2px solid #000;
    background: #eee;
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  .block-header {
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .annotation {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #444;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    border-left: 3px solid #666;
  }
  /* Specific blocks height to simulate layout */
  header.block {
    height: 70px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding-right: 2rem;
  }
  header .logo {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  nav {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  nav a {
    margin-left: 1.2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #000;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .hero.block {
    height: 250px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4caf50 0%, #81c784 100%);
    color: white;
    border-color: #4caf50;
  }
  .hero .cta-button {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    background: white;
    color: #4caf50;
    border: none;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    width: fit-content;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .hero .cta-button:hover {
    background: #c8e6c9;
  }
  .services.block {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  .service-item {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
    width: 28%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .service-item .icon-placeholder {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: #4caf50;
    margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }
  .service-item p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #333;
  }
  .call-to-action.block {
    height: 100px;
    background: #ff7043;
    color: white;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    border-color: #ff7043;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  footer.block {
    height: 60px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Wireframe Kasar Halaman Homepage</h1>
  <div class="wireframe-container">
    <header class="block header">
      <div class="logo">Logo Startup</div>
      <nav>
        <a href="#">Beranda</a>
        <a href="#">Layanan</a>
        <a href="#">Tentang Kami</a>
        <a href="#">Kontak</a>
      </nav>
      <div class="annotation" style="position:absolute; top:75px; left:0; width:100%; max-width:900px;">
        <strong>Header:</strong> Memuat logo dan navigasi utama yang mudah diakses pengguna untuk mengarahkan ke halaman penting.
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="block hero">
      <h2>Selamat Datang di Layanan Konsultasi Kesehatan</h2>
      <p>Mudah, cepat, dan terpercaya untuk kebutuhan kesehatan Anda</p>
      <button class="cta-button">Buat Janji Konsultasi</button>
      <div class="annotation" style="position:absolute; top:330px; left:0; width:100%; max-width:900px;">
        <strong>Hero Section:</strong> Menampilkan pesan utama dan call-to-action yang mencolok untuk mengundang pengguna memulai layanan.
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block services">
      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="icon-placeholder"></div>
        <p>Konsultasi Dokter</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="icon-placeholder"></div>
        <p>Resep Obat</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="icon-placeholder"></div>
        <p>Jadwal Kesehatan</p>
      </div>
      <div class="annotation" style="position:absolute; top:460px; left:0; width:100%; max-width:900px;">
        <strong>Layanan Utama:</strong> Menampilkan fitur atau layanan utama yang disediakan startup secara singkat dan mudah dipahami.
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block call-to-action">
      <span>Bergabunglah Sekarang dan Jaga Kesehatan Anda!</span>
      <div class="annotation" style="position:absolute; top:580px; left:0; width:100%; max-width:900px;">
        <strong>Call to Action:</strong> Bagian yang mengajak pengguna untuk mengambil tindakan yang diinginkan (sign up / buat janji).
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="block">
      &copy; 2024 Startup Konsultasi Kesehatan | Kontak: info@startupkesehatan.id
      <div class="annotation" style="position:absolute; top:660px; left:0; width:100%; max-width:900px;">
        <strong>Footer:</strong> Memuat informasi kontak dan hak cipta.
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
